  <name>FoFiX</name>
  <summary>Frets on Fire X: a fork of Frets on Fire with many added features and capabilities</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      This is Frets on Fire X, a highly customizable rhythm game supporting many modes of guitar, bass, drum, and vocal gameplay for up to four players. It is the continuation of a long succession of modifications to the original Frets on Fire by Unreal Voodoo.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Unique inverted keyboard gameplay style</li>
      <li>Support for guitar controllers and generic joysticks</li>
      <li>Includes a song editor for making your own tunes</li>
      <li>Compete with others on the World Charts</li>
      <li>Hundreds of songs composed by the community</li>
      <li>Supports importing Guitar Hero™ I and Guitar Hero™ II songs</li>
      <li>Multiplatform; runs on Windows™, Linux®, Mac OS X™ and FreeBSD®</li>
      <li>Open source, full Python source code available</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
